{"tid":278714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得鄭立呢返話算係摑咗讀垃圾科又想高人工既人一大巴?","createTime":"2017-06-10T16:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T05:58:45.000Z","uid":90577,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd861d9494005ccac1610be5bfa799b6886283fe","tid":278714,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T16:09:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497030853727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497030853727&d=P%2BV2fA6K%2BCQ20cZ1qX4pM%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=006e7632\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497030853727&h=0c3f633d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497030853727</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">工作4年月入1.1萬　大學生：養唔到家</span><br />\n<br />\nCheng Lap<br />\n4小時 &middot; <br />\n如果你想發財, 你就應該從商, 就算商人再怎樣被視為奸商, 不道德也好, 他們也是開宗明義牟利. 如果這樣也無法接受, 那靠從政, 教書, 當官, 宗教甚至慈善去發財, 豈非是邪魔歪道? 這些打從一開始就不是用來給你發財, 為何你會因此而發財?<br />\n<br />\n將段野改幾改,根本可以用來摑新聞中個班低薪大學生一大巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你想有高收入, 你就應該讀商科, 就算商科再怎樣被視為教人做奸商, 不道德也好, 他們也是開宗明義牟利. 如果這樣也無法接受, 那靠讀垃圾科去發財, 豈非是邪魔歪道? 這些打從一開始就不是用來給你發財, 為何你會因此而發財?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif